				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Great program slicer!  Here are a few things I would like to see:
<br />

<br />
1.)The ability to specify the IP of the machine you wish to sniff. (I REALLY need this feature  <img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" alt="Very Happy" border="0" /> )
<br />
2.)Expanded grouping capabilities. (similar to ShowEQ)
<br />
3.)The ability to have OE play a sound when an enemy realm enters your area.
<br />
4.)Some type of configuration file. (similar to SEQ)
<br />
5.)Experience window.  (again, similar to SEQ)
<br />

<br />
That is all I can think of at the moment.  I guess what I really want is as many features from SEQ as are possible.  I know that due to the differences in the 2 games, that some features aren't possible or even needed.
<br />

<br />
I know some of the things I mentioned have been listed by others, but I figured there would be no harm in listing it again. =)
<br />

<br />
Thanks again for devoting your time and energy to this great project.
<br />

<br />
Gimpzilla</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
